commit.message:
Query on call roster as at a specified time

Eg: `/oncall at 9am Sep 16th`
Use linked user handle instead of real name
Decrypt Slack API token during initialisation
Display roster end times using the timezone of the Slack user

Limit maximum attachments posted to Slack

https://api.slack.com/docs/message-attachments#when_to_use_attachments

Use different Slack and PagerDuty tokens for dev versus prod

It appears that serverless v1 beta has no support for deploying API
Gateway Stage Variables.
Add command to list escalation policies
Return usage example if command is incorrect
Respond to Slack before waiting for PagerDuty API response
